title = "Prisoner Manifest"
text = "Prisoner Manifest
XXXI May, MCXVIII

Cell A1: Relatively healthy male, age unknown. Recommended.

Cell A2: Healthy female, age 27. Minor behavioral issues, can be corrected at a later date. Recommended.
[PAGE]
Cell A3: Relatively healthy male, age 19. Exceptionally volatile. Futher correction will not prove useful. Disposed of.

Cell A4: Recently aquired healthy male, age unknown, likely 40s. Delayed recommendation until testing can be performed."
